						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up near a field called ‘Mañjayyabhaṭṭara-hola’.</p>						

						<p>[Sōyidēva ?] 1317 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record in characters of about the 14th century is dated the cyclic year <hi rend="bold">Dundubhi, [Jyēshṭha] śu. 15, Monday</hi> probably corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1322 A.D., May 31,</hi> when <hi rend="bold">Vīra Sōyidēva</hi> of the <hi rend="bold">Āḷupa</hi> family was ruling.</p>						

						<p>It seems to registers a gift of land probably by a lady. All details are lost.</p>						

						</summary>
					</msContents>
